data.description: Welcome to this beautifully renovated 4-bedroom, 3-full bathroom townhouse, boasting modern design and luxurious living. As you step inside, you're greeted by the expansive open floor plan, seamlessly connecting the living room to the dining area and kitchen, creating the perfect space for entertaining and everyday life.The heart of this home is the oversized kitchen peninsula, providing ample space for meal prep and casual dining. The kitchen itself is a chef's dream, with brand-new stainless steel appliances, sleek granite countertops, and an abundance of storage within the custom cabinetry. The LVP flooring throughout the main level not only adds elegance but also ensures durability and easy maintenance.One of the four spacious bedrooms is conveniently located on the main level, offering flexibility for guests or can be used as a home office or den. The full bathroom on this floor has been thoughtfully renovated with contemporary fixtures and finishes, adding a touch of sophistication.As you ascend to the upper level, you'll find the remaining three bedrooms, each featuring plush carpeting, generous closet space, and plenty of natural light. The master suite is a true retreat, complete with a large walk-in closet and a spa-like en-suite bathroom that has been fully updated to include a double vanity and premium tile work.With its prime location in a sought-after neighborhood, this move-in-ready home is a rare find. Don't miss the opportunity to make this stunning townhouse your new haven. Seller is willing to include HOME WARRANTY UP TO 2 YEARS as well!
